684
00:47:04,060 --> 00:47:06,060
I'm aware that you met...

685
00:47:06,460 --> 00:47:07,889
with Seo Hye Jin.

686
00:47:09,230 --> 00:47:10,330
Was Lee Jun Ho also there?

687
00:47:11,560 --> 00:47:12,600
Yes.

688
00:47:14,170 --> 00:47:15,199
