700
00:47:52,569 --> 00:47:53,600
However,

701
00:47:55,239 --> 00:47:56,710
it's been nearly a month...

702
00:47:57,810 --> 00:47:59,779
since your resignation was finalized.

703
00:48:01,250 --> 00:48:04,519
This isn't because I used to be a school teacher.

704
00:48:04,520 --> 00:48:07,020
Many good things happened to me...

705
00:48:07,719 --> 00:48:09,719
after you decided to join this academy.

706
00:48:11,290 --> 00:48:13,290
I'm grateful for that,

707
00:48:14,560 --> 00:48:18,360
and I believe all that's left is for us to focus on our teamwork.

708
00:48:19,199 --> 00:48:20,670
