709
00:48:22,069 --> 00:48:23,500
by acting this way.

710
00:48:25,869 --> 00:48:26,969
I don't follow.

711
00:48:28,839 --> 00:48:29,909
This...

712
00:48:30,779 --> 00:48:32,238
isn't a school...

