723
00:48:58,639 --> 00:49:00,068
Not her. She's doomed.

724
00:49:00,069 --> 00:49:01,408
Mom, please.

725
00:49:01,409 --> 00:49:02,739
Didn't you hear the rumor?

726
00:49:03,040 --> 00:49:04,409
Did you see it yourself?

727
00:49:04,580 --> 00:49:06,739
Did you see them in a compromising position?

728
00:49:06,909 --> 00:49:08,080
