775
00:51:52,409 --> 00:51:53,440
All right.

776
00:51:54,880 --> 00:51:55,980
I'll head out first.

777
00:51:57,179 --> 00:51:58,420
You should wrap up.

778
00:51:59,250 --> 00:52:00,279
Okay.

779
00:52:40,159 --> 00:52:41,489
