811
00:56:28,290 --> 00:56:30,319
I wanted to be with you today no matter what.

812
00:56:30,520 --> 00:56:31,889
But I can't say no to this appointment.

813
00:56:33,259 --> 00:56:34,389
Make sure to eat.

814
00:56:35,429 --> 00:56:36,489
