Mr. Lee...

819
00:57:15,469 --> 00:57:17,330
He's not an easy guy to handle.

820
00:57:18,069 --> 00:57:19,900
He stubbornly wrote this, so everyone could read it.

821
00:57:37,049 --> 00:57:38,889
I don't have to play with you today, right?

822
00:57:39,920 --> 00:57:41,330
Mr. Lee will call you, right?

823
00:57:42,489 --> 00:57:43,730
I have somewhere to be.

824
00:57:49,170 --> 00:57:50,199
Bye.

825
00:58:06,020 --> 00:58:07,650
Did your class go well today?

826
00:58:10,150 --> 00:58:11,159
Yes.

827
00:58:11,489 --> 00:58:12,520
What about Hye Jin's class?

828
00:58:20,830 --> 00:58:21,869
Did you know?

829
00:58:23,000 --> 00:58:25,238
When you wanted to join the academy,

830
00:58:25,239 --> 00:58:27,639
Hye Jin was dead set against it.

831
00:58:29,610 --> 00:58:30,839
I know about that.

832
00:58:33,310 --> 00:58:35,310
I should have listened to her.

833
00:58:36,949 --> 00:58:38,380
Had I done what she said,

834
00:58:39,119 --> 00:58:41,290
I would've easily gotten what I wanted.

835
00:58:51,199 --> 00:58:52,230
Thank you.

836
00:58:52,860 --> 00:58:55,000
You look so glum.

837
00:58:57,739 --> 00:58:59,069
It must be the lights here.

838
00:58:59,699 --> 00:59:00,770
I'm fine.

839
00:59:01,139 --> 00:59:02,610
Oh, aren't I glad to hear that?

840
00:59:40,239 --> 00:59:42,250
To catch the fish

841
00:59:42,380 --> 00:59:47,548
I am the romantic cat

842
00:59:47,549 --> 00:59:50,850
- What's going on? - The small, dancing starlight

843
00:59:50,949 --> 00:59:53,789
Shines on the sad city

844
00:59:53,790 --> 00:59:59,330
- I am the romantic cat - The romantic cat

845
00:59:59,460 --> 01:00:02,329
My sad, deep ocean

846
01:00:02,330 --> 01:00:08,139
Has left all alone

847
01:00:11,239 --> 01:00:12,310
Why aren't you singing?

848
01:00:18,480 --> 01:00:20,250
Was I mistaken?

849
01:00:21,089 --> 01:00:22,489
I thought instructors never did anything...

850
01:00:22,989 --> 01:00:24,690
that would risk them losing their voices.

851
01:00:25,619 --> 01:00:26,759
Gosh, we don't.

852
01:00:27,420 --> 01:00:28,489
Then what?

853
01:00:34,029 --> 01:00:35,069
Did something happen?

854
01:00:39,270 --> 01:00:40,770
It was a huge mess.

855
01:00:42,239 --> 01:00:43,339
I told you, didn't I?

856
01:00:43,739 --> 01:00:47,679
The hyenas would be attacking Mr. Lee and Ms. Seo.

857
01:00:48,179 --> 01:00:50,610
What does that have to do with you here,

858
01:00:50,710 --> 01:00:51,779
singing at the top of your lungs?

859
01:00:53,750 --> 01:00:55,549
I decided not to play their game.

860
01:00:58,389 --> 01:01:00,560
After deciding that, I felt somewhat liberated.

861
01:01:02,190 --> 01:01:04,460
I bet you're brimming with self-love too.

862
01:01:09,500 --> 01:01:11,540
After all that, I thought of...

863
01:01:12,639 --> 01:01:13,639
you.

864
01:01:19,810 --> 01:01:21,448
I used to think...

865
01:01:21,449 --> 01:01:24,580
it was ridiculous how people wasted their energy on dating or love.

866
01:01:29,250 --> 01:01:30,290
But not anymore?

867
01:01:32,259 --> 01:01:33,290
Well,

868
01:01:34,290 --> 01:01:35,830
after seeing Ms. Seo,

869
01:01:37,060 --> 01:01:40,029
I thought the contrary of my thought could be true.

870
01:01:47,270 --> 01:01:48,339
Let's get out of here.

871
01:01:50,239 --> 01:01:52,480
- I have ten minutes left. - Gosh.

872
01:01:53,009 --> 01:01:55,379
Unless you want me to confess to you under these lights,

873
01:01:55,380 --> 01:01:57,350
get your things now. All right.

874
01:01:58,850 --> 01:01:59,949
I don't care.

875
01:02:03,089 --> 01:02:04,619
- Do you mean that? - Yes.

876
01:02:05,489 --> 01:02:07,619
Personally, the content matters, not the form.

877
01:02:21,839 --> 01:02:23,040
I like you.

878
01:02:24,710 --> 01:02:25,810
You're cool.

879
01:02:26,409 --> 01:02:27,480
You make me...

880
01:02:28,779 --> 01:02:30,380
want to get to know you more.

881
01:02:35,619 --> 01:02:37,449
Going on a regular date like other couples will be hard.

882
01:02:38,920 --> 01:02:40,719
I'll always finish working in the middle of the night.

883
01:02:41,230 --> 01:02:42,759
I can't go to amusement parks on weekends either.

884
01:02:44,600 --> 01:02:46,130
On the days I teach for ten hours,

885
01:02:46,659 --> 01:02:48,299
I can't play with you because I won't have any energy left.

886
01:02:51,869 --> 01:02:53,199
I told you I had no problem playing alone.

887
01:03:24,799 --> 01:03:26,139
I didn't eat anything the whole day.

888
01:03:31,710 --> 01:03:33,739
(Daechi Chase)

889
01:03:51,060 --> 01:03:52,130
You know,

890
01:03:53,259 --> 01:03:55,429
I've been thinking.

891
01:04:03,339 --> 01:04:06,880
What do you think about leaving the academy?

892
01:04:13,779 --> 01:04:14,819
Well...

893
01:04:17,589 --> 01:04:18,619
If I do that,

894
01:04:20,460 --> 01:04:22,560
it will be the same as acknowledging the rumor to be true.

895
01:04:25,029 --> 01:04:27,759
Yoon Ji Seok has a good reputation among the instructors.

896
01:04:28,230 --> 01:04:29,500
He has influence too.

897
01:04:30,929 --> 01:04:35,069
If you leave, we might be able to calm him down for now.

898
01:04:35,869 --> 01:04:38,408
Anyway, I need to show him that...

899
01:04:38,409 --> 01:04:41,279
I am just as enraged about the recent incident.

900
01:04:43,549 --> 01:04:46,619
Please pardon my expression. But to make it effective,

901
01:04:47,020 --> 01:04:48,949
I should kick out Hye Jin.

902
01:04:51,389 --> 01:04:53,989
Don't look at me like that. I won't do that either.

903
01:04:55,929 --> 01:04:59,460
It's not like she can pursue another career path.

904
01:05:02,469 --> 01:05:04,699
How could I do that to her when I made her stay in this industry?

905
01:05:05,969 --> 01:05:07,040
I bought her a car.

906
01:05:07,670 --> 01:05:10,270
I helped her pay for her brother's tuition and gave her bonuses.

907
01:05:11,409 --> 01:05:13,610
I indirectly made her delay going back to school too.

908
01:05:14,339 --> 01:05:17,449
Then I made her miss the last bar exam.

909
01:05:22,619 --> 01:05:24,989
(Outline of the Administrative Law)

910
01:05:27,719 --> 01:05:28,889
But as for you,

911
01:05:29,630 --> 01:05:31,230
you can go anywhere you want.

912
01:05:32,799 --> 01:05:34,159
If you want, you can join a major academy.

913
01:05:34,529 --> 01:05:35,600
If you set your mind to it,

914
01:05:36,199 --> 01:05:37,869
you can get a job at a conglomerate again.

915
01:05:37,969 --> 01:05:39,869
Or you can take a break. You know?

916
01:05:39,969 --> 01:05:41,509
Your parents are well-off.

917
01:05:46,839 --> 01:05:49,479
Everyone in this neighborhood is throwing stones at her.

918
01:05:49,480 --> 01:05:50,750
And you want me to leave...

919
01:05:51,110 --> 01:05:53,919
I'm trying to pacify those people who are throwing stones at her...

920
01:05:53,920 --> 01:05:55,419
for Hye Jin's sake.

921
01:05:55,420 --> 01:05:56,489
I don't want to do that.

922
01:05:58,420 --> 01:06:00,420
I'll switch to a bigger academy someday.

923
01:06:01,589 --> 01:06:02,589
But not now.

924
01:06:04,900 --> 01:06:06,060
Gosh.

925
01:06:09,929 --> 01:06:12,040
I know that you're not affected by them.

926
01:06:13,540 --> 01:06:15,638
You weren't even embarrassed to show your report card...

927
01:06:15,639 --> 01:06:16,969
when you ranked in the eighth class.

928
01:06:19,779 --> 01:06:21,850
You're not even scared to work here...

929
01:06:22,049 --> 01:06:23,210
after quitting your job at that fancy company.

930
01:06:23,980 --> 01:06:26,079
Nothing in this world must scare you.

931
01:06:26,080 --> 01:06:27,119
No.

932
01:06:31,420 --> 01:06:32,489
I'm scared.

933
01:06:36,130 --> 01:06:38,529
I have never been as scared in my life as I am today.

934
01:06:39,460 --> 01:06:40,500
What do you...

935
01:06:56,009 --> 01:06:57,049
What...

936
01:07:02,690 --> 01:07:03,750
Ms. Seo...

937
01:07:10,560 --> 01:07:13,100
Everything she has done until now has broken down all at once.

938
01:07:20,670 --> 01:07:22,139
Gosh.

939
01:07:23,469 --> 01:07:25,278
I'm about to destroy the academy...

940
01:07:25,279 --> 01:07:27,139
I considered to be my alma mater.

941
01:07:29,250 --> 01:07:31,480
Okay. So...

942
01:07:37,750 --> 01:07:39,758
I keep trying to think of a way to fix this.

943
01:07:39,759 --> 01:07:41,560
But my mind keeps wandering.

944
01:07:48,770 --> 01:07:50,400
"Should I not have joined the academy?"

945
01:07:52,440 --> 01:07:54,469
"Should I have been nicer to my colleagues?"

946
01:07:55,239 --> 01:07:56,310
No.

947
01:07:57,009 --> 01:07:58,239
Listen. I'm trying to say...

948
01:07:59,080 --> 01:08:01,080
I also... Gosh.

949
01:08:02,250 --> 01:08:04,810
I also tried to find a way to fix this. You know?

950
01:08:08,750 --> 01:08:10,049
I'm a fool...

951
01:08:10,449 --> 01:08:13,420
who only thought about fulfilling my self-interest.

952
01:08:15,790 --> 01:08:17,230
So I'm so scared to death.

953
01:08:21,730 --> 01:08:22,969
Mr. Lee.

954
01:08:26,499 --> 01:08:27,940
Calm down.

955
01:09:08,379 --> 01:09:12,219
(The Midnight Romance in Hagwon)

956
01:09:12,379 --> 01:09:13,979
I'm embarrassed about everything that it's driving me crazy.

957
01:09:13,980 --> 01:09:15,388
You're the one who cried and acted like a baby.

958
01:09:15,389 --> 01:09:16,549
Why are you insulting me?

959
01:09:16,650 --> 01:09:18,589
"How would it have been if I wasn't your teacher?"

960
01:09:18,660 --> 01:09:20,190
"Then this kind of rumor wouldn't have spread."

961
01:09:20,459 --> 01:09:22,329
No one can voice their opinions to me about...

962
01:09:22,560 --> 01:09:24,230
how I run my business.

963
01:09:24,259 --> 01:09:26,759
Where are they? The people responsible for this incident.

964
01:09:26,929 --> 01:09:28,230
You really know nothing about this?

965
01:09:28,570 --> 01:09:29,999
I think there will be an offer.

966
01:09:30,829 --> 01:09:31,969
Come to your senses...

967
01:09:32,270 --> 01:09:33,469
before you sink any further.

968
01:09:33,700 --> 01:09:35,169
Who do you think has hit bottom?

969
01:09:35,270 --> 01:09:36,370
Have you lost your mind?

970
01:09:37,169 --> 01:09:39,810
Give it to me now. My well-deserved diploma.
